{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to chain or tether a dog",
        "additional_details": "Dogs are naturally social creatures who thrive on interaction with humans and other animals. Dogs tied up in one spot can suffer psychological damage.\r\n \r\nIt can also lead to injuries, and even death as it is possible for a dog to hang itself if the chain/tether is caught up something high.",
        "background": "Make it against the law for a dog to be tied up, whether the dog is being chained up or tethered.\r\n \r\nNo dog should be tied up for hours on end, as restricting a dog\u2019s freedom to move can be damaging to a dog\u2019s health, wellbeing and ability to properly socialise with humans and animals.",
